You see a short girl with long flowing brown hair and deep brown eyes.
In real life she is a unicorn with three forms..  Human, Unicorn, and
Panther.  She is a coaly black Unicorn with a golden mane and tail and a
black horn.  In Panther form she is the same coal black with golden
eyes.  She is very outgoing but has a short temper.  She is called
Blackmist because she never stays in one form for any length of time.

